                        "name": "justusw",
                        "displayName": "Justus Weber",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I'd like to note that the page loads successfully, the form element appears on the screen for a second, then disapears and is replaced by this error.  \nThe form element's label remains.  The Fatal Error stack trace is not viewable when looking at the page's source.",
